Class ParserUtilsSplitLineTest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class ParserUtilsSplitLineTest
extends junit.framework.TestCase
    Test the functionality of the splitLine method. This method returns a List of Strings. Each element of the list represents a column created by the parser from the delimited String.
